title: The Raccoon and The Chicken
itunes:title: The Raccoon and The Chicken
description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions

Edited by Diane Kang 

 

Leisha sang too hard at a party. Kate forgot about her house in Palm Springs.Then they come to the conclusion that raccoons indeed want the trash and they are indeed ready.
